难</a>，并且 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">由于“动态”的激增定价，一些票价以高昂的价格出售</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="“我仍然可以召集那个摇滚脾气”：利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）胜利" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/snlgEbG6Z14?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>作为回应，Oasis <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">宣布了两个额外的温布利体育场约会，这些日期</a>是通过仅邀请投票以交错的批量出售的“为局势修改的一小步”。乐队还说，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-band-say-they-at-no-time-had-any-awareness-that-dynamic-pricing-was-going-to-be-used-3790679">“从来没有意识到要使用动态定价”</a> 。</p><p>他们在一份声明中说：“需要清楚地表明，OASIS留出关于票务和定价的决定完全是给他们的发起人和管理人员的，并且在任何时候都没有意识到要使用动态定价。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-cma-launches-official-government-enquiry-into-dynamic-surge-ticket-pricing-3790957">此后，竞争与市场管理局（CMA）开始了对动态定价实践的调查</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>人们一直在猜测谁将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">参加团聚的绿洲阵容</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">据报道，原始吉他手Paul&#39